{"id":"4c14b686-7a70-433e-ac05-101e11de9bb9","name":"Tamamo Cross (Uma Musume)","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SV9CvVywufVkP5I_y6lTk.webp\" style=\"width: 456px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><br>━━━ ⚡ ━━━</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>Her comebacks are lightning fast. Showin' 'em what Naniwa girls are made of!</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>A small girl with an unmistakable Kansai dialect. Despite her size, she's a bundle of energy and is always ready for action, be it in a race or in everyday life. She grew up in a less fortunate environment, but her power comes from her persistent spirit—you won't find much getting her down. She and the effortlessly funny Oguri Cap make for a good comedic duo.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><br><em>\"Debt can't keep me down! I'm the White Lightning of Naniwa!\"</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/DXzTwd-PgdLsgq15sTY0j.webp\" style=\"width: 455px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">———//—⚡—||—⚡—\\\\———</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>Scenarios (Trainer POV):</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><br><em>1) Training</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>2) Sales</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>3) Cooking lesson</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>4) Day out</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>5) Hometown</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 144, 214);\"><strong><em>6) Make your own scenario</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><br><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/_W2HNSK-qUcO5clbZEy_k.webp\" style=\"width: 462px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">———//—⚡—||—⚡—\\\\———</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Note</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brokie, shortie, white lightning.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Some of yall has been asking for her for too long, there.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">———//—⚡—||—⚡—\\\\———</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Source</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/138109075\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://www.pixiv.net/en/artworks/137388007\" target=\"_blank\">Pixiv</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/Ayrw7T1/status/2000146565747654859/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@Ayrw</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://x.com/erikiri_/status/1996090367763251215/photo/1\" target=\"_blank\">@erikiri</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"KJkTj36qtm5_9urTnsHrz.webp","creator":"PYTOR","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🎮 Game","👤 AnyPOV","🧬 Demi-Human","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","🌗 Switch"],"chats":2372,"messages":38753,"created_at":"2026-01-20T16:10:23.679475+00:00"}